metadata.name: DDC #1
metadata.description:
Demon Death Cult: Season 1 is a collection of 50 unique, hand-drawn, 1/1, non-generative NFTs that exist on the Ethereum Blockchain, created by the artist Psychedemon.

Holding any DDC from Season 1 entitles you to automatic whitelist and one free mint for every Psychedemon project for the next 100 years. DDC holders also receive regular airdrop gifts, exclusive merch store access, and other valuable rewards and utility.

Join the Discord community and read the FAQ channel for more information here: https://discord.gg/ddc

Follow the project on Twitter: https://twitter.com/demondeathcult
